About Online Ordering






This extra special, one-time bottling of Van Winkle bourbon is bottled at 100 proof and comes in a handmade glass decanter from Glencairn Crystal Studio. Each bottle is individually numbered and labeled and includes a silver stopper and certificate of authenticity, all tucked inside a wooden box made from the oak staves of the barrels that aged this unique bourbon. The barrels were distilled in the spring and fall of 1989 and stored on the lower levels of a metal-clad warehouse built in 1935 at the Van Winkle family distillery in Shively, KY.





































